时，双击屏幕并从偶像设置中选择水成星町……</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.3o0wb1buaf4l-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.3o0wb1buaf4l-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.3o0wb1buaf4l-jpg.webp 500w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.3o0wb1buaf4l-147x300.webp 147w" width="500" height="1020" /></a></p><p>星町水成以AR方式出现在你的面前！</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.233h4xvgzmy2-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.233h4xvgzmy2-473x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 473px) 100vw, 473px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.233h4xvgzmy2-473x1024.webp 473w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.233h4xvgzmy2-139x300.webp 139w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.233h4xvgzmy2-jpg.webp 500w" width="473" height="1024" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.6dgtp8ewv81i-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.6dgtp8ewv81i-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.6dgtp8ewv81i-jpg.webp 500w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.6dgtp8ewv81i-147x300.webp 147w" width="500" height="1020" /></a></p><p>如果您从订单[歌曲]中选择“请！灰姑娘”，星町水成将随着德莱斯特的招牌歌曲跳舞。非常珍贵的景象！</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.wvt7el1qygji-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.wvt7el1qygji-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.wvt7el1qygji-jpg.webp 500w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.wvt7el1qygji-147x300.webp 147w" width="500" height="1020" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.x8kdgq6bg49u-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.x8kdgq6bg49u-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.x8kdgq6bg49u-jpg.webp 500w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.x8kdgq6bg49u-147x300.webp 147w" width="500" height="1020" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.qebvdwwt6qzc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.qebvdwwt6qzc-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.qebvdwwt6qzc-jpg.webp 500w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.qebvdwwt6qzc-147x300.webp 147w" width="500" height="1020" /></a></p><p>您可以按照[姿势]顺序摆出各种姿势。不愧是偶像，任何姿势都能完美驾驭。我什至在旅途中架起相机，给他们拍照。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/631b6862e05229b43c8f2fe1d4b55d13-kix.x3e44rteeb0w-jpg.webp" 